    This class is a subclass of the card class and it has only the number of card as an extra field.

    This class is for printing the output inside the cmd page.

    RunTest

    This is the main class of the program because it is a connection between the players and the cards and the methods and it is for playing the game.
    WildCard
    Wild cards can be use everywhere every time and they do things base on their type.
